messages.message: Hey, small UX thing I noticed. On this back button if you click somewhere on the page, but release over the button then it clicks it. I noticed this when I was accidentally doing it while highlighting the field name to delete and took a few times to realise what was going on
ah that’s confusing :disappointed: we’ll fix this bug!
@danny.lan i assume you don’t have capacity for this during this sprint? if so, i’ll take the ticket
